{
  "stem": "8784.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There were some attempts made to-- to-- permit us to submit names of people to the gathering places, so everybody would know if some relatives would arrive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But over the next few weeks while I was in-- in Krakow, Poland, I did not find anyone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I went back to my home where we lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I did not find anyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And after only a number of weeks after that, I was together with this girl, Anita Lampel, who was my close friend at that time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And we discovered that a transport is arriving from Mauthausen, and we had an idea that one of our buddies, Adam Mandel, whom I described before, was arriving in this-- possibly with the transport from Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And so we went to that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Both Anita and myself went to the school to search for this Adam Mandel when he arrives on this transport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And these people that arrived from Mauthausen were in such bad shape physically, almost emaciated people, nothing but skin and bones, that there was no way of recognizing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "If I was looking for this Adam Mandel, I would have not recognized him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "So I devised quickly a way that as we go through that room, we keep calling out, Adam, Adam, Adam.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And we walked through these bodies of people who were sitting on the floor, not able really to stand up, until one figure began to unwind from the floor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And he was a tall man, but because he was so thin-- nothing but skin on him, and bones-- at that time, he looked to me like a tremendously tall man by the time he unwound.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
